  "code": "%% B.Emergency Response System\nstateDiagram-v2\n    [*] --> Normal_Operation\n    Normal_Operation --> Warning_State: Minor Issue\n    Normal_Operation --> Critical_State: Major Issue\n    Warning_State --> Normal_Operation: Resolved\n    Warning_State --> Critical_State: Escalation\n    Critical_State --> Emergency_Landing: Cannot Resolve\n    Critical_State --> RTB: Can Return\n    Emergency_Landing --> [*]\n    RTB --> [*]",
