  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个应急响应系统的状态图，核心是从正常运营开始，根据问题严重程度分流到不同状态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Normal_Operation",
        "Warning_State",
        "Critical_State"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，那问题分级怎么定义？是分成轻微和严重两类，还是有更细的层级？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Minor Issue",
        "Major Issue"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "分两档就够了：Minor Issue触发Warning State，Major Issue直接进Critical State。Warning State里如果升级了，也能进到Critical State。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Warning_State",
        "Critical_State",
        "Escalation"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把主线画出来：初始状态指向Normal Operation，然后两条分支分别到Warning和Critical。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "[*]",
        "Normal_Operation",
        "Warning_State",
        "Critical_State"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Critical State后面要分两种情况：如果不能解决就Emergency Landing，如果能返航就RTB。这两个都是终态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Critical_State",
        "Emergency_Landing",
        "RTB",
        "Cannot Resolve",
        "Can Return"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下，Emergency Landing和RTB都直接结束，没有后续状态了对吧？另外Warning State除了升级，是不是也能恢复正常？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Emergency_Landing",
        "RTB",
        "[*]",
        "Warning_State",
        "Normal_Operation",
        "Resolved"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，Warning State问题解决后可以回到Normal Operation。两个终态都指向结束节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Warning_State",
        "Normal_Operation",
        "Resolved",
        "Emergency_Landing",
        "RTB",
        "[*]"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "画好了，整个流程从启动到正常运营，根据Minor/Major Issue分流，Warning可恢复或升级，Critical则决策着陆或返航，两个终态闭环结束。",
